{"id": 3045, "title": "Ticket #3045: Badly-formed XML causes problems in new ClassAd XML parser", "description": "<blockquote>\nSome varieties of invalid XML classad documents will send <code>classad::ClassAdXMLParser</code> into an infinite loop. One example is when content data is found outside of an attribute element, like so:\n<div class=\"code\">\n<pre class=\"code\">&lt;c&gt;ad&lt;/c&gt;\n</pre></div>\n\nThere may be other instances where an infinite loop can result.\n\n<p>Some varieties of invalid XML classad documents will cause <code>classad::ClassAdXMLParser</code> to leak memory. It returns immediately when it encounters the invalid input without deleting the <span class=\"wiki\"><a class=\"missing\" href=\"wiki?p=ClassAd\" title=\"Class Ad\">ClassAd</a></span> it's constructed so far.\n\n</p><p>Invalid input can also result in the parser returning a partially-constructed <span class=\"wiki\"><a class=\"missing\" href=\"wiki?p=ClassAd\" title=\"Class Ad\">ClassAd</a></span> without indicating there was an error or trying to read to the end of the enclosing classad element.</p></blockquote>", "remarks": "<blockquote>\n<hr/>\n<em>2012-Aug-23 14:10:41 by zmiller:</em> <br/>\n\nBulk change of target version from v070802 to v070803 using ./ticket-target-mover.</blockquote>", "derived_tickets": "", "attachments": "<html><head></head><body></body></html>", "check_ins": "<table border=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\">\n<tbody><tr><td align=\"right\" valign=\"top\" width=\"160\">2012-Jun-20 10:37</td>\n<td align=\"center\" valign=\"top\" width=\"30\">\n<span class=\"icon dot\">\u00a0</span></td>\n<td align=\"left\" valign=\"top\"> \nCheck-in <span class=\"chng\"><a href=\"https://github.com/htcondor/htcondor/commit/515c18c61550e67b125db468aa1b0f1778d1e81d\">[32424]</a></span>: minor 7.8.2 version history item edits for combination item. ===GT=== <span class=\"ticket\"><a class=\"resolved\" href=\"/wiki-archive/tickets/?ticket=3049\" onclick=\"get_ticket_and_populate_wrapper('3049'); return false;\" title=\"Some versions of ClassAdXMLParser::ParseClassAd() don't work\">#3049</a></span> ===GT=== <span class=\"ticket\"><a class=\"resolved\" href=\"/wiki-archive/tickets/?ticket=3042\" onclick=\"get_ticket_and_populate_wrapper('3042'); return false;\" title=\"New ClassAd XML parser ignores leading whitespace in string values\">#3042</a></span> ===GT=== <span class=\"ticket\"><a class=\"resolved\" href=\"/wiki-archive/tickets/?ticket=3045\" onclick=\"get_ticket_and_populate_wrapper('3045'); return false;\" title=\"Badly-formed XML causes problems in new ClassAd XML parser\">#3045</a></span>  (By Karen Miller )</td></tr>\n<tr><td align=\"right\" valign=\"top\" width=\"160\">2012-Jun-12 14:50</td>\n<td align=\"center\" valign=\"top\" width=\"30\">\n<span class=\"icon dot\">\u00a0</span></td>\n<td align=\"left\" valign=\"top\"> \nCheck-in <span class=\"chng\"><a href=\"https://github.com/htcondor/htcondor/commit/cf670b51a314bd507a9470f924df86b9b02f625c\">[32283]</a></span>: Add XML parsing fixes to version history. <span class=\"ticket\"><a class=\"resolved\" href=\"/wiki-archive/tickets/?ticket=3042\" onclick=\"get_ticket_and_populate_wrapper('3042'); return false;\" title=\"New ClassAd XML parser ignores leading whitespace in string values\">#3042</a></span> <span class=\"ticket\"><a class=\"resolved\" href=\"/wiki-archive/tickets/?ticket=3045\" onclick=\"get_ticket_and_populate_wrapper('3045'); return false;\" title=\"Badly-formed XML causes problems in new ClassAd XML parser\">#3045</a></span> <span class=\"ticket\"><a class=\"resolved\" href=\"/wiki-archive/tickets/?ticket=3049\" onclick=\"get_ticket_and_populate_wrapper('3049'); return false;\" title=\"Some versions of ClassAdXMLParser::ParseClassAd() don't work\">#3049</a></span>  (By Jaime Frey )</td></tr>\n<tr><td align=\"right\" valign=\"top\" width=\"160\">2012-Jun-11 10:39</td>\n<td align=\"center\" valign=\"top\" width=\"30\">\n<span class=\"icon dot\">\u00a0</s